items.name: Transformers Fanon Wiki
items.title: Transformers Fanon Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Transformers Fanon Wikia!
items.desc:
The Transformers Fanon Wikia, commonly called Transfanon, is a wikia for making up transformers characters, story lines, or anything else Transformers related. Everything here is non-canon! None of it is real! 

We allow users to make their own stories without them being deleted like they would be on the Transformers Wiki. They would only be deleted if they have offensive text or have no purpose and have little sense (Joke Articles are an exception).

Happy editing!

items.name: Transformers2005 MUSH Wiki
items.title: Transformers2005 MUSH Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to one of the longest running Transformers RPGs of all time!
items.desc:
The death of Unicron was merely the beginning... Thirty years have passed since the events of Transformers: The Movie, and the galaxy spanning war between the noble Autobots and evil Decepticons has become more brutal than ever...

Welcome to the home of Transformers 2005, a text based RPG based on Cybertron’s own Robots in Disguise! We operate on a MUSH (Multi User Shared Hallucination- the original MMO!), using a balance of coded systems and collaborative storytelling to create a unique (and kind of addicting) role playing experience.

Join one of the longest running online RPGs as an Autobot, Decepticon, Junkion, or even a soldier of the Earth Defense Command and help shape the future of the Transformers!

items.name: UK Transport Wiki
items.title: UK Transport Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the UK Transport Wikia
items.desc: The UK Transport Wiki is what you want it to be - we host all content relating to transport in United Kingdom and Ireland only. The UK Transport wiki is place where everyone's welcome, and every vistor can edit! Since we started in March 2008, we've generated 1,837 articles for you! You can also join the behind the wiki on Facebook! or view the photo site at The UK Transport Photos Site

items.name: Transformice Wiki
items.title: Transformice Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Transformice Wiki
items.desc: Transformice is a free online multiplayer game created by Melibellule and Tigrounette owned by Atelier 801. The objective of this game is to collect cheese playing as a mouse character, and take it back to the hole in exchange for a currency, not surprisingly named cheese. This cheese can be spent on items, map creation or other things, such as starting up a tribe of mice. In the majority of maps, a shaman is needed to aid in getting the mice to the cheese and into the mouse hole, using wide selection of tools that can be conjured by the shaman to create various contraptions to get to the cheese.

items.title: Transformer: Prime Wiki
items.headline: Stay tooned for season 3!
items.desc: Welcome to the Transformers: Prime Wiki, a comprehensive database and collaborative encyclopedia, created by the fans, for the fans, that houses information on all aspects of the CGI animated series: Transformers: Prime and the Aligned continuity family of the Transformers franchise. Our mission: to collaborate with other fans in order to build a reliable, accurate encyclopedic resource with as much detailed information about the TV shows, comics, books, films, games and merchandise related to the Aligned continuity as possible.  Everyone is welcome to join in and contribute here, as long as edits are constructive and relevant to the continuity.

items.headline: Spend a night at the Hotel Transylvania Wiki
items.desc:
Welcome to Hotel Transylvania Wiki, a collaborative encyclopedia for everything and anything that is related to the Hotel Transylvania franchise.

Hotel Transylvania is a computer-animated 3D comedy film produced by Sony Pictures Animation for Columbia Pictures and released on September 28, 2012, and featuring the voices of Adam Sandler, Selena Gomez, Andy Samberg, Kevin James, Fran Drescher, Jon Lovitz, Cee Lo Green, Steve Buscemi, Molly Shannon and David Spade.

items.headline: Transformers Legends Wiki
items.desc: A collaborative community site about Transformers Legends. Transformers Legends is an electronic card battle game which you can assemble a team of powerful Transformers characters and battle with your friends. You can customize and power up your Transformers team with credits, cards, and battles. You can either defend the world with the Autobots or destroy it with the Decepticons.
